content:
Keeps Prisma client in sync with schema changes and automatically creates database migrations. Validates schema syntax and generates TypeScript types for type-safe database access.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *schema.prisma ]]; then echo 'üîÑ Syncing Prisma schema...' && npx prisma validate && npx prisma format && echo 'üìù Generating Prisma client...' && npx prisma generate && echo 'üóÑÔ∏è Creating migration...' && npx prisma migrate dev --name auto_migration --create-only && echo '‚úÖ Prisma sync complete - Review migration before applying' || echo '‚ö†Ô∏è Prisma sync failed - check schema for errors'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
